text:
Very friendly staff.
Freshly made waffle with fruits was a hit.
Best part they have fresh coconut juice too.
For the health conscious families who don't want to eat burger or fries can drop by here to try the varieties available compared to other options nearby.

Bought an Espresso Frappuccino. This is a probably the most diluted coffee one can buy anywhere in the world. Absolutely bland.  Let my family verify and even my boys could hardly taste the coffee. Informed the staff n given a bigger straw to drink it. I like his humour.

Luv - Grind with love! We ordered two flat whites, was horrible for 6$ each. They are doing a disservice by having the coffee as the theme on their branding and the fantastic Nuova Simonelli coffee machine!
